column2: IDEA-180073 PlatformTestCase fails with "Code style settings damaged"

column3:
Unknown elements should be cloned during a "copyFrom"
operation, otherwise reading code style settings from
disk, then cloning, results in the cloned instance
being different that the instance read from disk
(if some elements are unknown).

This happens 100% of the time after running Android
Studio from intellij because Android Studio adds
elements that are unknown to the settings used
in PlatformTestCase.
Already fixed, thanks for the PR.
